Chorizo, egg & cheese breakfast burrito

Initial version:
Drop in about.. 
1/4 lb chorizo with a small splash of olive oil. Get it frying..
Crack a couple eggs in a cup, shake in a little salt.
When the chorizo is done add in the two scrambled eggs. Get this frying..
When this is about done toss in a handful of grated cheese. get this frying..
Squirt in a little Tapatio sauce.
When the cheese is melted in..
Fill a tortilla with the mixture and enjoy. Typically makes 2 burritos.

Very tasty!
